# Dynamic Shop Implementation Plan

The objective is to refactor the "Sacred Gemstones" Shop page so that products are fully dynamic. The admin will be able to add, edit, and delete gemstones directly from the Dashboard.

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Database Schema (Firestore)
Create a new `products` collection with the following document structure:
- `name`: String (e.g. "Natural Ruby (Manik)")
- `price`: String (e.g. "₹25,000+")
- `desc`: String (e.g. "Boosts confidence...")
- `image`: String (Base64 encoded string, using the same free local upload technique we just built!)
- `createdAt`: Timestamp

